<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>, uns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gut frewnde die von Erffurt von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der sich von
                            <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geselle<ex>n</ex></expan> an <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan> iren
                                <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> hat,
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        irs briefs, wir ewch ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, daran ir der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von Erffurt
                            <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>. Was nu ewr <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        in den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> sein welle, des lat uns ewr
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Denn wo wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
